metadata.name: Legend of $PEPE
metadata.description: Once upon a time, in a kingdom far, far away, there lived a brave knight named Pepe. Pepe was known throughout the land for his bravery and his unwavering dedication to serving his kingdom. However, Pepe had always dreamed of traveling to the moon. He had heard tales of its beauty and wonder, and he longed to see it for himself.... To be continued
